# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [0.5.7] ## 2022-10-31
### Changed
- Bump to a custom version of tract 0.18.3 (fix infinite loop when loading some models)

## [0.5.6] ## 2022-10-24 (MISFIRED)
### Added
- Models unused will now be deleted, if the setting is specified in the server configuration file.

### Changed
- Bump to tract 0.18.3

## [0.5.5] ## 2022-10-13
### Added
- Namespacing support

### Changed
- Bump to a new custom version of tract 0.17.2

## [0.5.1] ## 2022-09-11
### Added
- Model sealing can be disabled

### Changed
- Bump to custom version of tract 0.17.2
- The real error message was never sent if the stream was cancelled by the server
- Code refactoring

## [0.5.0] ## 2022-09-09
### Added
- Support of JWT attestation
- Automatic detection of the input type and size of models
- New telemetry system
- Model sealing

### Changed
- Bump to tract 0.17.2
- Error messages are now explicit
- No longer using serde_cbor for data serialization/deserialization

## [0.4.0] ## 2022-08-02
### Added
- Multiple models support. The server can now have in memory more than one model at a time. 
- Multiple inputs supports. The user is now able to give multiple inputs to the models.

### Changed
- Increase enclave max memory to 2.4gb
- Bump to a customized version of tract 0.17.2

## [0.3.0] ## 2022-03-25
### Added
- Now support sending signed responses to the client.
- Added an endpoint to get the server version.
- Disable debug in policy.toml generation for hardware mode.
- Added intergration testing.

### Changed
- Protobuf files were changed, not backward-compatible.
- Optimized docker image sizes.
- Allow changing the tensor output type.
- Changed telemetry.
- Update some dependencies.

## [0.2.2] ## 2022-03-02
### Added
- Support of remote attestation of Azure DCs_v3 VMs (this is a workaround as Azure PCS is sending expired collateral/keys).
### Changed
- Cleaned up attestation crate and fixed potential Undefined Behavior in the quote verification function.
- Upgraded Rust toolchain of the untrusted part to nightly-2021-11-01

## [0.2.1] ## 2022-02-24
### Changed
- Cleaned up warnings, used cargo fmt.

## [0.2.0] ## 2022-02-22
### Added
- Added telemetry. Can be disabled by setting the environment variable ```BLINDAI_DISABLE_TELEMETRY``` to ```1```.

## 2022-02-16
### Changed
- Changed the docker building process to enable reproducible builds.

## [0.1.0] - 2022-02-15
### Added
- Initial release
